Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.45,0:22:33.94,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,Everyone smiles at the beautiful girls
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.94,0:22:34.83,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「my dream！」
